    "recommended_first_use": "Use the open pack for AI platform architecture review, then attach the evaluator to MCP gateway decisions and customer pilot telemetry.",
    "sales_motion": "Lead with the open trust-fabric pack, then sell hosted customer-specific trust scoring, policy adapters, signed verdicts, SOC export, and trust-center evidence APIs."
  },
  "executive_readout": {
    "board_level_claim": "SecurityRecipes can reduce agent adoption friction by turning many scattered agent safety controls into one inspectable trust verdict per run.",
    "recommended_first_use": "Use the open pack for AI platform architecture review, then attach the evaluator to MCP gateway decisions and customer pilot telemetry.",
    "why_it_is_differentiated": "Most agent guidance stops at controls. The trust fabric composes generated evidence into an allow, hold, deny, or kill decision that agents and auditors can consume."
